What is Software Testing?
A: doing testing for making the software bug free

Why do we need Automation?
A: manual is too slow so automation makes it easier.

What is selenium?
A: manual work done by selenium, as it becomes automated.

Selenium RC     >outdated
Selenium IDE    >its like plugin/extension for browser  (doesn't has much power)
Selenium Grid   >to run tests on multiple machines  (not learning from Syntax)
Selenium Webdriver  >to interact with browsers

How to reload dependencies when face issues in pom.xml file?
A: pom.xml file is a management dependency file. Go to pom.xml > maven > reload project
